OL,3,CThug who used festival-goer as 'cash
OL,4,Ccow' before murdering him jailed
OL,6,FA homeless man who used a holidaymaker
OL,7,Fas a "cash-cow" to fund a drink and
OL,8,Fdrugs session then bludgeoned him to
OL,9,Fdeath, has been jailed for a minimum
OL,10,Fof 31 years.
OL,12,FDrug addict Anthony Roberston, 33,
OL,13,Fbefriended middle-aged holidaymaker
OL,14,FCharles Adair after they randomly met
OL,15,Fin Skegness town centre one evening
OL,16,Fsometime between 30 June and 2 July
OL,17,Flast year.
