OL,6,FThe pair then spent the night together
OL,7,Fdrinking and buying drugs, funded by
OL,8,FMr Adair, who was in the resort to
OL,9,Fattend a music festival.
OL,11,FThe men visited several bars, houses
OL,12,Fand shops that evening before they
OL,13,Fwere seen entering scrubland on
OL,14,FRichmond Drive, near Tesco.
OL,16,FThis is where Robertson beat his
OL,17,Fvictim to death, shattering his skull
OL,18,Fwith a large rock. He was seen some
OL,19,Ftime later leaving the area on his own.
