OL,6,FLincolnshire Police received a report
OL,7,Fof a body on the scrubland on just
OL,8,Fafter midnight on 3 July and
OL,9,Fsubsequently launched a murder
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FA post-mortem examination confirmed Mr
OL,13,FMcGhee Adair, 59, had serious head
OL,14,Finjuries including "extensive"
OL,15,Ffractures and deep lacerations to his
OL,16,Fface which a pathologist said had been
OL,17,Fcaused by "multiple" blunt force
OL,18,Ftraumas.
