OL,3,CThug who used festival-goer as 'cash
OL,4,Ccow' before murdering him jailed
OL,6,FFollowing a complex investigation,
OL,7,FRobertson, of no fixed address, was
OL,8,Fidentified through CCTV, located, and
OL,9,Farrested on suspicion of murder. He
OL,10,Fwas charged with murder, robbery, and
OL,11,Ffraud by misrepresentation.
OL,13,FRobertson, who initially denied any
OL,14,Finvolvement, had pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Fmanslaughter at a previous hearing.
OL,16,FBut on Friday, 2 February, the jury at
OL,17,FLincoln Crown Court found him guilty
OL,18,Fof murder and robbery. He had
OL,19,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to fraud.
