OL,6,FOn Monday, 5 February, victim impact
OL,7,Fstatements from Mr Adair's family were
OL,8,Fread out during the sentence hearing.
OL,10,FMr Adair's son, also called Charlie
OL,11,FAdair, said the premature taking of
OL,12,Fhis father's life had robbed him of
OL,13,Fthe opportunity to develop their
OL,14,Frelationship and with his
OL,15,Fgrandchildren.
OL,17,FMr Adair's sister, Catherine, said a
OL,18,Fdark cloud had come over the whole
OL,19,Ffamily since her brother's death.
