OL,6,FThe jury at Lincoln Crown Court took
OL,7,Fjust over an hour to find Robertson
OL,8,Fguilty of murder after a three-week
OL,9,Ftrial. They also convicted Robertson
OL,10,Fof a second charge of robbery relating
OL,11,Fto Mr Adair on the same date.
OL,13,FJailing Robertson, Judge Smon Hirst
OL,14,Fsaid: "This was a murder committed for
OL,15,Fgain."
OL,17,FDet Ch Insp Jen Lovatt, from East
OL,18,FMidlands Special Operations Unit,
OL,19,Fsaid: "Robertson clearly used Mr Adair
OL,20,Fto fund his night out during which he
OL,21,Fwas bought alcohol, food, and drugs.
