OL,3,CThug who used festival-goer as 'cash
OL,4,Ccow' before murdering him jailed
OL,6,F"Robertson used his victim as a cash-
OL,7,Fcow and aimed to obtain as much money
OL,8,Ffrom him as possible. Adair was set to
OL,9,Fleave Skegness later the day he died
OL,10,Fand would have ended Robertson's cash
OL,11,Fflow, leading to the attack. He
OL,12,Fclearly set out to exploit Mr Adair's
OL,13,Fgenerosity.
OL,15,F"Our investigation showed that
OL,16,FRobertson used his victim's bank card
OL,17,Fafter death. Robertson sold the
OL,18,Fvictim's phone without his knowledge
OL,19,Fduring the evening prior to his death.
