OL,4,Ccow' before murdering him jailed
OL,6,F"This was a vicious attack in which
OL,7,FRobertson beat Mr McGhee Adair and
OL,8,Fleft him for dead. He stole his wallet
OL,9,Fcontaining his bank card which he used
OL,10,Fseveral times and also stole his
OL,11,Fmobile phone.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts are with Mr McGhee
OL,14,FAdair's family at this difficult time.
OL,15,FHe was a much-loved grandad, dad, and
OL,16,Ffriend to many."
